title: Head of Female
description:
Terracotta head, female. Hair braided in horizontal braids down each side of face and tied in high knot, encircled with band, on top of head. Details of back of head incised. Pierced at ears. Probably from a statuette. Cast hollow from two part mould. 
Condition: Good.
credit_line: Gift of Evangeline Wilbour Blashfield, Theodora Wilbour, and Victor Wilbour honoring the wishes of their mother, Charlotte Beebe Wilbour, as a memorial to their father, Charles Edwin Wilbour
